dct_title_s: Bayview to Bay Head along Barnegat Bay
dct_description_sm: Map shows grants and leases along Barnegat Bay and the Rivers and Creeks. Grants go from the vicinity of the town of Bayview, north to Bay Head. Map also shows towns and waterways.
